271
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:15,280
No, no, no, no.

272
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:16,160
No way, man.

273
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:17,260
This is impossible!

274
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:18,900
I don't get it!

275
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:20,210
