285
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:10,550
Why do I have to change myself?

286
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:12,200
Besides, the usual pattern is...

287
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,560
It's gone!

288
00:16:13,560 --> 00:16:15,130
