294
00:16:29,050 --> 00:16:30,670
I'm starting to get pissed off.

295
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:32,130
I'll beat him awake!

296
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:36,240
Damn, I look fine!

297
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,530
I can't hit that face!

298
00:16:37,530 --> 00:16:38,630
I mean, it's me!

299
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:42,350
But what am I supposed to do then?!

300
00:16:42,950 --> 00:16:45,680
What's with all the noise this early?

301
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:47,820
Sadaharu, what are you doing?

302
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:48,830
Kagura!

303
00:16:48,830 --> 00:16:50,420
Perfect timing!

304
00:16:50,930 --> 00:16:52,510
What's wrong, Gin-chan?

305
00:16:52,510 --> 00:16:54,700
Did you finally snap?

306
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,660
You're acting funny.

307
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:57,140
That's right, Kagura!

308
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:58,150
Way to notice!

309
00:16:58,150 --> 00:16:59,110
Look over here!

310
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:00,120
Gin-chan's over here!

311
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:02,860
Though Gin-chan's also over there,
but Gin-chan's also over here!

312
00:17:00,470 --> 00:17:02,360
You hung over?

313
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,000
And something stinks.

314
00:17:05,360 --> 00:17:06,700
