315
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:07,880
No!

316
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,270
You can't go to the living room right now!

317
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:12,940
That Sadaharu, or it was me, I guess...!

318
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:22,680
Gin-chan...

319
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:25,460
This is beyond sad.

320
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:28,090
I would hope that you could
clean up after yourself.

321
00:17:28,090 --> 00:17:30,900
And could you stay away from
me for the time being,

322
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:32,180
