323
00:17:32,180 --> 00:17:33,400
You've got it wrong!

324
00:17:33,610 --> 00:17:35,630
You should know, Kagura-chan!

325
00:17:35,630 --> 00:17:38,540
Gin-san may be a slob, but he knows
how to keep his stuff inside!

326
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:40,170
He keeps his ass tight and shut, too.

327
00:17:40,170 --> 00:17:41,890
It's me, but it's not my fault!

328
00:17:41,890 --> 00:17:44,300
Sadaharu, what are you trying to say?

329
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:47,520
Hurry over here before you catch
his bed-shitting habits, Sadaharu.

330
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:51,420
I wasn't talking to you!

331
00:17:51,650 --> 00:17:54,410
Gin-san! I mean, Sadaharu!

332
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:56,970
Good morning.

333
00:17:56,970 --> 00:17:58,600
Sh-Shinpachi!

334
00:17:58,600 --> 00:18:01,130
You should be able to notice
the problem here!

335
00:18:01,130 --> 00:18:03,020
You've been with me since
the first episode!

336
00:18:03,020 --> 00:18:05,480
I'm sorry about calling
you a lame four-eyes!

337
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:08,540
Those glasses are the glasses
of truth which reveal all!

338
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:10,040
What's wrong, Sadaharu?

339
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:11,430
And something stinks.

340
00:18:11,430 --> 00:18:13,460
What's this smell?

341
00:18:21,530 --> 00:18:25,020
Gin-san, I was already
disappointed in you,

342
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:27,440
but I wasn't expecting you to get worse.

343
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:30,080
You've reached a new low.

344
00:18:30,290 --> 00:18:32,400
You better clean this yourself.

345
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,750
What? He's looking down on me?

346
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:36,580
Kagura-chan, let's go kill time
at Otose-san's place.

347
00:18:36,580 --> 00:18:37,850
Let's.

348
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:40,260
We'll catch his bed-shitting
habits if we stay here.

349
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:41,590
Shitface.

350
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,840
Sadaharu...

351
