352
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:51,170
How can you humiliate me when we've
only switched places for a little...

353
00:18:51,170 --> 00:18:52,830
Switched places...

354
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:54,600
That's it!

355
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:57,650
A switch can be resolved by
falling down a set of stairs!

356
00:18:57,650 --> 00:19:02,660
That's been the typical method
used to end these stories!

357
00:19:14,930 --> 00:19:17,390
I-It didn't fix anything!

358
00:19:22,320 --> 00:19:24,270
Good timing, Zura!

359
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:25,980
Stop that guy!

360
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:29,030
They say that a boy can transform
himself in three days...

361
00:19:29,030 --> 00:19:32,900
Haven't you changed in some way?

362
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:34,520
Yes! That's right!

363
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:36,670
I knew you would understand!

364
00:19:36,670 --> 00:19:40,260
Well, we shouldn't stand here and talk
so let's find a place to sit down.

365
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:43,150
Though it may take a shake
or two to find a spot,

366
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:47,660
but it's better than standing around
like we're trying to play dead.

367
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:49,310
What are you doing, Zura?!

368
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:52,020
How dare you use your conversation
to manipulate me!

369
00:19:52,020 --> 00:19:55,680
In that case, I'll use gestures or pantomime
to tell him what's going on!

370
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:57,710
Well, Sadaharu-dono...

371
00:19:57,710 --> 00:19:58,250
Creepy!

372
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,480
Stop, Zura!

373
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,650
Such a cutie.

374
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,650
[Note: Masanori Hata (a.k.a Mutsugoro) is a writer and naturalist. He was an owner of "Mutsugoro Kingdom", a ranch with various animals.]

375
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,650
Why the Mutsugoro-san impression?!

376
00:20:01,650 --> 00:20:05,340
Can I fluff your stomach?

377
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:07,150
Stop!

378
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:09,930
I don't wanna admit it!
Don't wanna admit it!

379
00:20:09,930 --> 00:20:11,370
But it feels so good!

380
00:20:11,370 --> 00:20:11,950
So good!

381
00:20:11,950 --> 00:20:14,570
No! No! Yes!

382
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:16,940
What a lovely day.

383
00:20:17,910 --> 00:20:20,880
