384
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,980
Wait, Sadaharu?

385
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:25,370
Damn it! Where'd that bastard go?!

386
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:30,540
What's with the penetrating look?

387
00:20:30,540 --> 00:20:32,170
You're not your usual self.

388
00:20:32,170 --> 00:20:33,590
I love it!

389
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:35,160
You're making me numb!

390
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:37,490
Look down on me as much as you want!

391
00:20:37,490 --> 00:20:38,770
Step on me!

392
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:42,380
I'm a poor little bitch who
