395
00:20:52,890 --> 00:20:53,600
Very well!

396
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:55,910
I'll accept whatever you have to give!

397
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:59,010
Bring it on!

398
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:02,070
Hurry!

399
00:21:02,070 --> 00:21:02,820
Come!

400
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,820
