409
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:38,400
I may have changed on the outside, but
my soul will continue to shine brightly!

410
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,860
For eternity!

411
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:43,600
Man, I'm, uh, you're taking this in stride...

412
00:21:45,410 --> 00:21:46,800
Gin-san.

